en_189750_0	The new State Ministers and Deputy Ministers will be sworn in at the Presidential Secretariat this morning (May 02).
en_189750_1	The swearing-in ceremony will commence at 10.30 am.
en_189750_2	All Ministers and MPs of the government have been requested to be present for this.
en_189750_3	Eighteen new Cabinet Ministers were sworn in before President Maithripala Sirisena at a ceremony held at the Presidential Secretariat yesterday.
en_189750_4	The President Media Division said that the other Cabinet Ministers will continue to serve in their existing portfolios.
